Interface GetIterableElementsOperation<SEED_TYPE,RETURN_TYPE>

  • Type Parameters:

    RETURN_TYPE - the result type of the operation. This must be JSON serialisable.

    public interface GetIterableElementsOperation<SEED_TYPE,RETURN_TYPE>
extends GetIterableOperation<SEED_TYPE,RETURN_TYPE>, GetElementsOperation<SEED_TYPE,CloseableIterable<RETURN_TYPE>>
    A GetIterableElementsOperation defines a seeded get operation to be processed on a graph, resulting in an Iterable of Element objects.
